{
  "texts": [
    "For example, clicking on an educational source is considered an action for users.",
    "Also, for each user, u ∈ U is a sequential time window as W u = {w 1 u, w 2 u, w 3 u,.",
    ", w t u} which t represents the total number of time windows; Also, w t u shows a col- lection of smaller time units as w t u = {d 1, d 2,.",
    ", d x } where x indicates the length of time windows.",
    "Moreover, the related items of the user (u) in time windows (t) express by w t u."
  ]
}